  <p>Passing under a magnificent lemon tree, you enter this spacious guest room located on the ground floor, a lovely room decorated in the colors of Provence. There is direct access to the garden.</p>
  <p>In this cosy room with sloping ceilings and exposed beams, there is either a King Size bed or two twin beds based on your preference. A sitting area, a desk, a shower room and a separate toilet complete this junior suite.</p>
  <p>Decorated in the Provençal style, the Niçoise junior suite will immediately transport you in the atmosphere of Old Nice, capital of the French Riviera.</p>
